	[build]: Kill off `GROFF_GHOSTSCRIPT_AVAILABILITY_NOTICE`.

	* m4/groff.m4 (GROFF_GHOSTSCRIPT_AVAILABILITY_NOTICE): Delete.
	* configure.ac: Stop interpolating same.

