	(pushBackBuffer::pushBackBuffer): Add `const` qualifier to `char
	*` argument.

2025-05-19  G. Branden Robinson <g.branden.robinson@gmail.com>

	* src/preproc/html/pre-html.cpp (imageList::createImage)
