2024-12-21  G. Branden Robinson <g.branden.robinson@gmail.com>

	* src/utils/hpftodit/hpftodit.cpp (main):
	* src/utils/indxbib/indxbib.cpp (main):
	* src/utils/lkbib/lkbib.cpp (main):
	* src/utils/lookbib/lookbib.cpp (main):
