	Drop now-unused Autoconf macros.

	* configure.ac: Stop expanding `GROFF_AWK_NOTICE`,
	`GROFF_PDFROFF_DEPENDENCIES_CHECK`, and
	`GROFF_PDFROFF_PROGRAM_NOTICE` macros.  Drop `AM_CONDITIONAL`
	with `USE_PDFROFF` argument.
